snippet.title: J-Town: A Visual Novel || LAUNCH TRAILER
snippet.description:
Download and play for free now! 
Steam:https://store.steampowered.com/app/2413310/JTown_A_Visual_Novel/
itch.io: https://iszacstartown.itch.io/j-town-a-visual-novel

A friendly crash course in Japanese American history, culture, and community! Inspired by the real stories of the three historic Japantowns of California: San Francisco, San Jose, and Los Angeles's Little Tokyo.

Follow us on our socials! 
https://twitter.com/JTownVN
https://www.instagram.com/jtownvn/

Funded on Kickstarter
